sections.text:
(a)    In addition to the bond required under § 5-102 of this subtitle, the State Treasurer shall be covered by a surety bond as required in this section.

(b)    The surety bond under this section shall:

(1)    be conditioned on the faithful performance of the duties of the State Treasurer as custodian of the Unemployment Insurance Fund;

(2)    run to the State;

(3)    be in an amount that the Secretary approves; and

(4)    be in a form required by law or approved by the Attorney General.
